titles.title: A bill to renew the previously existing suspension of duty on parts of aircraft generators.

action.text: Sponsor introductory remarks on measure. (CR S16456)
Read twice and referred to the Committee on Finance.

bill.summary: 11/19/1993--Introduced. Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to extend, through December 31, 1994, the suspension of duty on aircraft generator parts.
